{"title":"夜过韶关车站（外二首）","authors":["钱英球"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":1,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜过韶关车站"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱英球"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个解冻的湖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮在日夜澎湃；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步的浪花推涌着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喧腾在繁忙的站台。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信号灯举起希望之星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着一个赶路的时代；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜路已经走完，心的东山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正上升着彤红的未来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罱沙船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船在江面颠荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心在浪尖颠荡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两支长长的竹篙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捞着星月，捞着太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捞起来了，沉甸甸的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是失落了的希望……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同那个沉淀了的梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也一起捞到了船上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北江之秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披两岸五彩的时装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲的河笑得好欢畅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身体有点儿消瘦了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可比过去更加匆忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长长的船队载着什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红砖，新瓦，秋粮……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有那清亮清亮的山歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有那重新抽芽的信仰。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}